fields.name: dino
fields.description: Dinos are from an ancient era and will make a unique and engaging pet!

fields.name: lizard
fields.description: Loyal but timid, a lizard will make an excellent pet if you want cool, but quiet!

fields.name: monkey
fields.description: Choosing a monkey will mean a companion for life, but don't try to be their owner! Having a monkey is a partnership.

fields.name: mouse
fields.description: Mice are playful and exciting! Scampering around and chasing them will become a part of your daily routine.

fields.name: tapir
fields.description: Tapirs are a sort of unusual pet. They will love you, but keep an eye out around them! They tend to be troublesome!

fields.name: Fifty Shades of Beige by Eel Jame

To Injure a Mimicbird by Luter Lee
Sprite's Sprouts
fields.description: Full of organic fruits and vegetables, sure to keep your pets well nourished and healthy, even though everything seems to have a very slight coating of dirt.

fields.name: Borders
fields.description: Oh, you're looking for books? You've come to the right place! We are going out of business soon so all books are half price!

fields.name: Traditional Herbs
fields.description: Create the life you were born to live. Ancient fixes proven to cure the mind, body, and spirit. The healing power of nature can get you past any sickness.

fields.name: Alchemist
fields.description: Give your pet new life. Purify and perfect all imperfections. Potions guaranteed to have desirable effects on all pets, young and old.

fields.name: Shop Plush
fields.description: Find your new furry friend at Shop Plush (TM)!

fields.name: Quick Trip
fields.description: Your one-stop-shop for any foods that are "guaranteed" to be good and good for you! No refunds!

fields.name: Announcements
fields.description: Find out all the latest happenings on the Primaria announcements boards. Only staff are allowed to post topics, but anyone may comment.
